    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">Restore the protective DWR (durable water repellency) coating on high-tech rainwear or snow gear with Revivex Durable Water Repellent. This spray-on treatment repels water, oil and stains. It can also be used for tent reproofing. Over time the DWR of outerwear and camp gear wears off. Regular reproofing treatment of jackets, tents, and other gear is highly recommended. The durable formula creates a water repellent coating that stays on even after a wash. Choose the size that’s right for you (10.5 oz or 16.9 fl oz) and ensure peak performance by pre-washing garments with Revivex Pro Cleaner. This formula is ideal for use on waterproof-breathable fabrics like event®, NeoShell®, and GORE-TEX® fabric</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n\n  \n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-repe