.9 fl oz) and ensure peak performance by pre-washing garments with Revivex Pro Cleaner. This formula is ideal for use on waterproof-breathable fabrics like event®, NeoShell®, and GORE-TEX® fabric. For all types of reproofing projects, use Revivex Durable Water Repellent and get protection all season long.</p>\n\n\n\t\t\t  <h3>Product Details</h3>\n\t\t\t  <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n\t\t\t  <div class=\"product-specs\">\n\t\t\t\t  <table>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">MPN:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">MCN</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">UPC:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">021563362268</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Restore water repellency on GORE-TEX® jackets, bibs, ski pants, gloves, drysuits and waders; add repellency to nylon tent flies, down jackets and backpacks</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Spray on this long-lasting formula that’s washable and provides all-season protection from water, oil and stains; one 10.5 oz spray can treat 2-4 jackets</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Maximize breathability and enhance performance of all types of waterproof-breathable fabrics using this DWR spray; also available in 16.9 fl oz bottle</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Use the air-powered sprayer to easily disperse every last drop of the PFOA, PFOS and silicon free formula</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">Packaging may vary</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  </table>\n\t\t\t  </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t  </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t  <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t  <p>© 2026</p></div></div>",
